# DescribeDay(day)
- IF: ${day == 1 || day == "1"}
    - Monday
- ELSEIF: ${day == 2 || day == "2"}
    - Tuesday
- ELSEIF: ${day == 3 || day == "3"}
    - Wednesday
- ELSEIF: ${day == 4 || day == "4"}
    - Thursday
- ELSEIF: ${day == 5 || day == "5"}
    - Friday
- ELSEIF: ${day == 6 || day == "6"}
    - Saturday
- ELSEIF: ${day == 7 || day == "7"}
    - Sunday
- ELSE:
    - I cannot present you the data, because it is incorrent.
# SendActivity_ISAD3p()
